items.title: WATCH:  'Kitty Fat Camp' helps overweight cats find homes
items.description: ABC News' Danny New talks to one woman who is helping overweight felines shed pounds and live healthier lives.

items.title: WATCH:  Pancake ice blankets Lake Michigan
items.description: Drone footage shows pancake ice rolling over waves on Lake Michigan.

items.title: ABC News Exclusive: Former Uvalde officer speaks out after acquittal
items.description: Adrian Gonzales said he stood by his actions and argued he was scapegoated by prosecutors looking for someone to blame.

items.title: Europe must 'play the power game' with Trump over Greenland, former Danish FM says
items.description: Former Danish Foreign Minister Jeppe Kofod told ABC News that Europe must meet U.S. threats over Greenland with strength.

items.title: WATCH:  Over 160 million Americans prepare for "potentially catastrophic" winter storm
items.description: The winter storm stretches over 2,000 miles from New Mexico and Texas all the way to Maine. Several states have declared a state of emergency.
